{"tid":1544892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想玩清朝債券呢張好牌，其實做一樣野就得","createTime":"2019-09-05T17:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T03:39:48.000Z","uid":306748,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"00d813c1254293b812a24ec453f37459b9f71c59","tid":1544892,"uid":306748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:05:37.000Z","msg":"見到有人開post講過呢件野，但大家都好似唔知點玩，又或者錯左focus。呢張牌嘅重點，並唔係要香港歸英或者歸台，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而係要觸發中共支爆</span></span></strong>。因為一日唔支爆，中共咁強硬，答應五大訴求可能性係0，更加唔好講脫離中共。大家可以睇下面呢篇文章<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei-com.cdn.ampproject.org/wp/s/martinoei.com/article/28633/清朝債券-與香港主權/amp?usqp=mq331AQQKAFwAZgB4fj88fXLvp3nAQ%3D%3D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fwp%2Fs%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F28633%2F%E6%B8%85%E6%9C%9D%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8-%E8%88%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%2Famp%3Fusqp%3Dmq331AQQKAFwAZgB4fj88fXLvp3nAQ%253D%253D&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=9d8cfeb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei-com.cdn.ampproject.org/wp/s/martinoei.com/article/28633/清朝債券-與香港主權/amp?usqp=mq331AQQKAFwAZgB4fj88fXLvp3nAQ%3D%3D</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單來講，中國還錢會立即支爆；唔還的話會有幾個可能的結局，上文只講左一個，但呢個並唔重要，因為中共肯定會賴皮唔放香港，到時候全世界就大條道理制裁佢鎖佢國，以中共宜家的情況都係會支爆。換句話說，呢張牌一出，中共死撚硬。<br />\n<br />\n我地諗到嘅野，侵侵一早已經諗到，只不過佢宜家係欠缺左出師的藉口。所以我地香港人可以做嘅野只有一樣，就是<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求美國重新審視香港主權<br />\n要求美國重新審視香港主權<br />\n要求美國重新審視香港主權</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為清債問題所以全世界宜家知道中共係非法霸佔中國，換句話說中共97亦無權收番香港，所以要求美國重新審視香港主權係好合理。只不過無香港人嘅請求，美國好難主動去幫香港審視主權。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以908美領要大叫呢句口號，之後不斷twitter啲美國政客宣傳開去。</span></span></strong>記住唔洗講多，廢除中英聯合聲明之類的唔洗提，因為我要真普選前提係一國兩制，講呢句會俾人話有抵觸。謹記我地目的係支爆從而令到五大訴求實現，歸英歸台港獨係bonus之後先再算。同時要繼續宣傳Chinazi，只要全世界人越討厭中共，就會越支持制裁中共。<br />\n侵侵肯定已經準備好晒，只要佢出到師，除左等睇支爆，香港人基本上都唔使做啲乜。無成本又可以觸發支爆嘅野，大家真係唔做？"},{"pid":"86d882ee67d732aa914d86bfab2c25d7b2964363","tid":1544892,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80dea442f3141a809e88314c5c449a8c3717c7a8","tid":1544892,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:06:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31a0275cf0defc1041ed6cb4c1fe6ace9ed25898","tid":1544892,"uid":306748,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"我係大陸做野嘅朋友同我講，大陸宜家糧食唔夠，暴動四起，庫房被清空，過度借貸，好多人無工開，只有大城市先睇落仲係安定。基本上已經差唔多到黃巾之亂嘅地步，佢直頭覺得中共過唔到十一，所以自己都急急腳都走番去美國。大家以為支爆好遙遠，但實情係就快爆，作為一個愛國者係咪好應該推佢一把呢？"},{"pid":"44796b1eb4b98cc52ac0644be2cada5961bd0b0a","tid":1544892,"uid":224479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"s